{"tid":2000567,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有公務員指全面復工有助處理積壓的工作","createTime":"2020-05-04T03:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T03:30:09.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"91c7253c1997eb813028081dfce341404eafc807","tid":2000567,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T03:11:10.000Z","msg":"香港公務員今日大致全面復工，在政府總部外，有之前一直都上班的公務員表示，較早前並非全部同事上班，部分工序受阻，認為全面復工有助處理積壓的工作。<br />\n<br />\n亦有公務員表示，部分工作不能在家進行，同事全數上班能跟進自己工作。亦有人說，之前由於不清楚其他部門人員有沒有上班，聯絡時會有困難。<br />\n<br />\n有公務員表示，部門未有提供口罩，但巿面已能購買，不太擔心防疫裝備問題。有人就仍然擔心疫情，因為不會知道誰人已受到感染。亦有公務員認為是時候全面復工，不能停擺太久。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1524091-20200504.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1524091-20200504.htm&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX6Ggm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=ad08b22e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1524091-20200504.htm&h=ab225a85\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1524091-20200504.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7c173dcafbd661d57a030ef070c854941c4715","tid":2000567,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T03:11:57.000Z","msg":"我的訴求係返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe043b04b88703e5aa8affc4659d02d975a22446","tid":2000567,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T03:30:09.000Z","msg":"公務員有三種<br />\n第一種係高級+一級多位過二級夠期就有得